title: Galaxy Browns | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
We break down the fantasy implications from the highly anticipated Cowboys-Patriots game and discuss whom you should actually start against New England's stout defense (3:00). Then we buy tons of stock in the Browns against Miami, find a secret gem at tight end, and build our daily fantasy lineup for the weekend (19:30).
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
